    "code": "arr = fnp.arange(24).reshape((2, 3, 4))\n\nfnp.unstack(arr)\n\nfnp.unstack(arr, axis=1)\n\narr2 = fnp.stack(fnp.unstack(arr, axis=1), axis=1)\n\narr2.shape\n\nfnp.all(arr == arr2)",
